T1  - Rational Bubbles in UK Housing Markets: Comment on “No-Bubble Condition: Model-Free Tests in Housing Markets”
AU  - Domeij, David
AU  - Ellingsen, Tore
Y1  - 2020/07/01
PY  - 2020
DA  - 2020/07/01
